commit.message: Fixes #9 #10 adding support for testserver command

Merge pull request #7 from cderwin/test_alternate_runners

Test alternate runners
Install all requirements for testing and set the PYTHONPATH environment variable so subprocesses (in particular on Travis CI) search the right path
Add tests for django-nose and update runtests.py accordingly

Fixed #5 -- Add support for `django-nose` and any other custom test commands.

* Add a `TEST_WITHOUT_MIGRATIONS_COMMAND` setting that should be a dotted path
  to a management command class to use as a base class, to which we will add
  the `-n` and `--nomigrations` arguments.

* Remove `-n` and `--nomigrations` from `sys.arg`, in case we are extending a
  custom that passes these along.

Change flag -nm to -n

It seems that optparse used in django 1.7 demands 
1 char short flags.

Merge pull request #4 from grantmcconnaughey/master

Add -nm alias

Merge pull request #1 from deniscostadsc/patch-1

Fix link for number of PyPI downloads
